Package: TCRtools
Title: Helper functions for analyzing TCR sequence data from single-cell RNA-seq.
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Dufort", email = "matt.dufort@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package includes a number of functions for manipulating and/or analyzing TCR sequences from single-cell RNA-seq data. It is a work in progress, with new functions being added regularly to expand functionality and simplify existing processes.
Imports:
	stringr,
	checkmate
Suggests:
	circlize
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
